headline: Is Kroger (KR) Pricing Look Justified After Strong Multi Year Share Price Gains
summary: If you are wondering whether Kroger is fairly priced at today’s levels, you are not alone. This article will walk through what the current share price might be implying about its underlying value. Kroger’s stock recently closed at US$71.25, with returns of 5.6% over 7 days, 12.8% over 30 days, 13.2% year to date, 11.6% over 1 year, 73.0% over 3 years and 132.9% over 5 years.
